data.description: Great County Home has lots of potential! Large rock ranch style home boast over 3200 square Feet. Home has 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, 2 car garage and two car- carport. Out buildings and barns. Fenced, pond, and water well. Great country location with mature oaks. Breckenridge schools, only 9 miles North of Ranger. Back pasture great for horses. Has large garden area, chicken coops and more. Rooms are oversized and have potential to add another bedroom and bath.
